      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "1. Updating the assessment of the operational environment and the performance of the Nepal power sector, institutional setup, its future plans, and long term sustainability; problem tree analysis.\r\n2. Carrying out the necessary surveys to establish baseline data in the project areas.\r\n3. Assessment of the procurement and implementation capacity of Nepal Electricity Authority (NEA) considering each of the divisions handling the subprojects and prioritization of the subprojects.\r\n4. Estimation (or review) of the foreign and local costs, taxes and duties and contingencies for each of thes ubprojects; Package contracts for goods and services economic and financial viability asessment, financial projects for NEA and assessment of its past financial performance and financial management systems.\r\n5. Review safeguard documentation for subprojects, carry any additional safeguard assessments and preparation of associated plans."
